summary: This Public Domain Agreement outlines the terms between Ninu, Inc. (Nimia) and users downloading public domain content from Nimia's website.  The agreement dictates permitted uses of the content, primarily prohibiting resale, redistribution in certain formats, and extraction of original files.  Nimia provides the content "as is" with limited warranties, and users indemnify Nimia against any legal action arising from content use.  The agreement includes clauses on termination, replacement content, and liability limitations ($10,000 maximum).  Disputes are to be resolved through arbitration in Seattle, Washington.
